data.description: Come and see this pristine conditioned home today! As you enter, you will notice that the floor plan is open, which creates a very spacious feel throughout! The rooms are also separated, making for privacy for each person. This home hosts 1,262 sq. ft. a 2 car garage, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, an amazing kitchen with a bar and a screened in porch, that is great for family time and relaxation. This home also has a fenced in back yard, which is great for privacy! Be sure to schedule a time to see this home now, you don't want to miss out on your chance to own it for you and your family! This home is legible for 100% financing through the Community Homeownership Incentive Program (CHIP).
